The paper discusses the use of spiking neural networks for clustering and classifying image data, which falls under the categories of neural networks (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of inhibition strategies and evaluation rules, which could potentially fall under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
